<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Explore India — TripAdvisor</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f7f8fa;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --ink: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #8a8a8a;
      --accent: #00AA6C;
      --accent2: #34E0A1;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --green-grad: linear-gradient(135deg, #00AA6C 0%, #34E0A1 100%);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── DOT BG ── */
    .dot-bg {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: -1;
      background-color: #f0f2f5;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #c8cdd6 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 24px 24px;
    }

    /* ── NAVBAR ── */
    .navbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .navbar-inner {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 6vw; height: 64px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--accent2);
      border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; font-size: 17px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(52,224,161,0.35);
    }
    .nav-logo span {
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .nav-logo span b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex; gap: 28px; list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links li {
      font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: #4a4a4a;
      cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links li:hover, .nav-links li.active { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .greeting-pill {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      background: rgba(52,224,161,0.1);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.2);
      border-radius: 100px; padding: 5px 14px;
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent);
    }
    .avatar {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: var(--green-grad);
      border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.9rem; color: white;
      text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,170,108,0.35);
    }
    .avatar:hover { transform: scale(1.08); }
    .btn-profile {
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.35); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 7px 16px; text-decoration: none; background: white;
      transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-profile:hover { background: rgba(0,170,108,0.07); }
    .btn-logout {
      font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #8a8a8a;
      text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px;
      border: 1.5px solid #d4d4d4; border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-logout:hover { border-color: #e05252; color: #e05252; }
    .btn-signin {
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 6rem 6vw 5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0fdf8 55%, #e6fdf5 100%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(52,224,161,0.15);
    }
    .hero-bg-circle {
      position: absolute; top: -80px; right: -80px;
      width: 420px; height: 420px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,224,161,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-bg-circle2 {
      position: absolute; bottom: -60px; left: -60px;
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,170,108,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(52,224,161,0.1);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.2);
      border-radius: 100px; padding: 5px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 9vw, 7.5rem);
      font-weight: 300; line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink);
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.35s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title em {
      font-style: italic;
      background: var(--green-grad);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 1.8rem;
      max-width: 500px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 500;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.5s forwards;
    }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.65s forwards;
    }
    .hero-stat-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .hero-stat-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; right: 6vw;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1s forwards;
    }
    .hero-scroll-line { width: 36px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent2); }

    /* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
    .section-header {
      padding: 4rem 6vw 2rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .section-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

    /* ── PLACES ── */
    .places {
      padding: 0 6vw 6rem;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }

    .place {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0 3rem;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      align-items: start;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .place.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .place-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--accent); padding-top: 0.4rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .place-info {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem;
    }

    .place-state {
      font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;
    }

    .place-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .place-divider {
      width: 1.5rem; height: 2px;
      background: var(--green-grad);
      border-radius: 2px; margin: 0.2rem 0;
    }

    .place-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem; color: #6a6a6a;
      line-height: 1.85; max-width: 380px; font-weight: 500;
    }

    .place-tags {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem; margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .tag {
      font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.25);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(52,224,161,0.06);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .tag:hover { background: rgba(52,224,161,0.15); border-color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── IMAGE ── */
    .place-img-wrap {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 12px; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .place-img-wrap img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
      display: block; transition: transform 0.6s ease;
      filter: brightness(0.96) saturate(1.05);
    }
    .place:hover .place-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.05); filter: brightness(1) saturate(1.1); }
    .img-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .img-badge {
      position: absolute; bottom: 0.75rem; left: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: white; font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(0,170,108,0.75);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 100px;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: white;
      padding: 2.5rem 6vw;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .footer-brand {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink);
    }
    .footer-brand b {
      background: var(--green-grad);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .place { grid-template-columns: 2rem 1fr; }
      .place-img-wrap {
        grid-column: 1 / -1; margin-top: 1.5rem; aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      }
      .place-info { padding-right: 0; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .places { padding: 0 5vw 4rem; }
      .section-header { padding: 3rem 5vw 1.5rem; }
      .hero { padding: 4rem 5vw 3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- DOT BACKGROUND -->
<div class="dot-bg"></div>

<!-- ══════════ NAVBAR ══════════ -->
<header class="navbar">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <a href="/home" class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-icon">🦉</div>
      <span>Trip<b>Advisor</b></span>
    </a>

    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li onclick="window.location.href='/home'">Home</li>
      <li class="active">Explore</li>
      <li>Reviews</li>
      <li>About</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="nav-right">
      <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
        <span class="greeting-pill hidden-sm">👋 Hey, <%= user.name.split(' ')[0] %>!</span>
        <a href="/profile" class="avatar" title="Profile"><%= user.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() %></a>
        <a href="/profile" class="btn-profile">👤 Profile</a>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout">Logout</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login" class="btn-signin">Sign In</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-bg-circle2"></div>

  <p class="hero-tag">🌍 Explore — India</p>
  <h1 class="hero-title">The<br /><em>Sub&shy;continent</em><br />Awaits</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Eleven destinations across the length and breadth of India — from Himalayan valleys to desert forts, colonial waterfronts to ancient ruins.</p>

  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">11</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Destinations</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">8</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">States</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">∞</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Memories</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span class="hero-scroll-line"></span>
    Scroll to explore
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION HEADER -->
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="section-label">11 Destinations</span>
  <div class="section-line"></div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════ PLACES ══════════ -->
<section class="places">

  <!-- 01 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">01</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Uttar Pradesh</p>
        <h2 class="place-name"><a href="/varanasi" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.25);transition:border-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#00AA6C'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,170,108,0.25)'">Varanasi</a></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">One of the oldest inhabited cities on Earth, Varanasi lines the sacred Ganges with ancient ghats. At dawn, pilgrims descend into golden light and rising incense smoke — a ritual unchanged for millennia. To witness it is to feel time bend.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Spiritual</span>
        <span class="tag">Ghats</span>
        <span class="tag">Ancient</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://s7ap1.scene7.com/is/image/incredibleindia/manikarnika-ghat-city-hero?qlt=82&ts=1727959374496" alt="Varanasi ghats at dusk" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Varanasi, UP</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 02 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">02</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Rajasthan</p>
        <h2 class="place-name"><a href="/jaisalmer" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.25);transition:border-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#00AA6C'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,170,108,0.25)'">Jaisalmer</a></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">The Golden City rises from the Thar Desert like a mirage, built almost entirely of honey-yellow sandstone. Its towering fort still houses a living community, and beyond the city gates lie endless dunes where the silence is absolute.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Desert</span>
        <span class="tag">Fort</span>
        <span class="tag">Architecture</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://www.historyhit.com/app/uploads/bis-images/5153617/Jaisalmer-Fort-1-788x537.jpg?x15201" alt="Jaisalmer Fort" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Jaisalmer, RJ</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 03 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">03</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Karnataka</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Hampi</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">A UNESCO World Heritage Site scattered across a surreal boulder landscape, Hampi was once the capital of the Vijayanagara Empire. Temples, chariot streets, and ruins stretch across miles of rust-red rock under an open sky.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">UNESCO</span>
        <span class="tag">Ruins</span>
        <span class="tag">Temples</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://thefederal.com/file/2022/09/Hampi.jpg" alt="Hampi Virupaksha Temple" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Hampi, KA</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 04 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">04</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Himachal Pradesh</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Spiti Valley</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">A cold desert mountain valley perched above 4,000 metres, Spiti is austere and breathtaking. Ancient Buddhist monasteries cling to cliff faces, the air is thin and crystalline, and the night sky is unlike anything else in India.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Mountains</span>
        <span class="tag">Buddhism</span>
        <span class="tag">Offbeat</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://bloominghimalaya.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiti.jpeg" alt="Kee Monastery Spiti Valley" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Spiti, HP</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 05 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">05</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Kerala</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Kochi</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">Shaped by centuries of Arab, Chinese, Portuguese, Dutch, and British presence, Kochi carries its layered history lightly. Chinese fishing nets line the waterfront, spice markets perfume the air, and Fort Kochi's lanes feel like a quiet world apart.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Heritage</span>
        <span class="tag">Seafood</span>
        <span class="tag">Backwaters</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/de/f0/eb/backwater-tourism.jpg?w=700&h=-1&s=1" alt="Chinese Fishing Nets Kochi" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Kochi, KL</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 06 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">06</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Arunachal Pradesh</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Ziro Valley</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">Hidden in the eastern Himalayas, Ziro is a lush plateau home to the Apatani tribe and their remarkable terraced rice fields. One of India's most undervisited places, it rewards the journey with misty hills and living traditions.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Tribal Culture</span>
        <span class="tag">Nature</span>
        <span class="tag">Offbeat</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://www.naturetravelagency.com/uploads/1730551339Ziro%20Valley%20resort.jpg" alt="Ziro Valley rice terraces" loading="lazy"
        onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=800&q=80'" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Ziro, AR</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 07 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">07</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Puducherry</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Pondicherry</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="place-divider"></div>
      <p class="place-desc">A former French colony where bougainvillea spills over mustard-yellow walls, Pondicherry is unlike any other Indian city. The White Town grid of wide colonial avenues meets Tamil quarters in a collision of cultures that somehow feels utterly serene.</p>
      <div class="place-tags">
        <span class="tag">Colonial</span>
        <span class="tag">French Quarter</span>
        <span class="tag">Beaches</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="place-img-wrap">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/Pondicherry_streets.jpg/1280px-Pondicherry_streets.jpg" alt="Pondicherry French Quarter streets" loading="lazy"
        onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582510003544-4d00b7f74220?w=800&q=80'" />
      <div class="img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="img-badge">Pondicherry, PY</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 08 -->
  <div class="place">
    <span class="place-num">08</span>
    <div class="place-info">
      <div>
        <p class="place-state">Gujarat</p>
        <h2 class="place-name">Rann of Kutch</h2>
      </div>
